①：If this card is in your GY and you control "Junk Warrior" or a monster that mentions it, except "Anchorbolt Hedgehog" (Quick Effect): You can Special Summon this card in Defense Position, also you cannot Special Summon from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn, except Synchro Monsters.

name: Synchro Fellows
desc:
You can only activate 1 card with this card's name per turn.
①：Add 1 "Junk Synchron" and 1 monster that mentions "Junk Warrior" or "Stardust Dragon" from your Deck to your hand, then discard 1 card.
②：You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 Synchro Monster you control; decrease its Level by 1, then, during your Main Phase this turn, you can Normal Summon 1 "Synchron" monster in addition to your Normal Summon/Set. (You can only gain this effect once per turn.)

name: Junk Warrior Extreme
desc:
"Junk Synchron" + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
You can only use this card name's ① and ② effects once per turn each.
①：If this card is Synchro Summoned: You can Special Summon as many Level 2 or lower monsters from your GY as possible, but their effects cannot be activated for the rest of this turn, also you can only Special Summon once for the rest of this turn.
②：When this card destroys an opponent's monster by battle: You can banish this card; Special Summon 1 "Junk" Synchro Monster from your Extra Deck. (This is treated as a Synchro Summon.)

name: Nurikabe
desc:
You can only use the effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If this card is in your GY, except the turn it was sent there: You can pay 1000 LP, then target 1 other Zombie monster in your GY; Special Summon it and this card, but their effects are negated, also banish them when they leave the field.

name: Dragonic Warrior
desc:
You can only use the effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：You can discard 1 card; Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower Dragon monster from your hand or Deck, except "Dragonic Warrior", but its effects are negated.

name: Einroid
desc:
You can only use the effect of this card's name once per turn.
①：If this card is destroyed by battle or card effect: You can send 2 Level 4 or lower Machine monsters from your Deck to the GY.

name: Soul Union
desc:
You can only activate 1 card with this card's name per turn.
①: Target 1 face-up monster on the field and 1 "Elemental HERO" monster in your GY; that monster on the field gains ATK equal to the ATK of other monster (until the end of this turn), then, if you have an "Elemental HERO" Normal Monster on your field and/or in your GY, you can Fusion Summon 1 "Elemental HERO" Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, by banishing its material from your GY.

name: Prima Light
desc:
You can only use 1 of the ① and ② effect of this card's name per turn, and only once that turn.
①: Activate 1 of these effects;
● Tribute 1 EARTH Warrior monster, and if you do, Special Summon 1 LIGHT Warrior monster from your hand or Deck.
● During the Main Phase: Immediately after this effect resolves, Normal Summon 1 Warrior monster from your hand.
②: During your Main Phase: You can banish this card from your GY; add 1 Warrior or Fairy "Cyber" monster from your Deck to your hand.

name: Conduction Warrior Linear Magnum ±
desc:
Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned (from your hand) by sending 2 "Magnet Warrior" monsters whose original Level is 4 or lower from your hand, Deck, and/or face-up field to the GY. You can only Special Summon "Conduction Warrior Linear Magnum ±" once per turn this way. You can only use the ① and ② effect of this card's name each once per turn.
①: You can target 1 other EARTH monster on the field; this card gains ATK equal to half that monster's until the end of this turn.
②: If this card is destroyed and sent to the GY: Add it to your hand.

name: Chaos Distill
desc:
You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①: Any card sent to your GY is banished instead.
②: You can activate 1 of these effects;
● Add 1 "Macro Cosmos", or 1 card that mentions it, from your Deck to your hand, except "Chaos Distill".
● If "Macro Cosmos" is on the field: Banish this face-up card from the Spell & Trap Zone; add 1 LIGHT monster with ? ATK from your Deck to your hand.

name: Hero's Rule 1: Five Freedoms
desc:
You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①: Target up to 5 cards in any GY(s); banish them.
②: If this card is in your GY, except the turn it was sent there: You can banish it, then target 1 of your banished "Elemental HERO" monsters; Special Summon it, ignoring its Summoning conditions.

name: Archfiend Matador
desc:
You can Ritual Summon this card with "Ritual of the Matador". You can only use the ① effect of this card's name once per turn.
①: If this card is Ritual Summoned: You can add 2 "Archfiend" cards from your Deck to your hand, except "Archfiend Matador", also this card cannot attack this turn.
②: Cannot be destroyed by battle, also you take no battle damage from battles involving this card.
③: If this card battles a monster, after damage calculation: Destroy that monster, and if you do, inflict 1000 damage to your opponent.

name: Ritual of the Matador
desc:
You can only use the ② effect of this card's name once per turn.
①: Ritual Summon 1 "Archfiend Matador" from your hand, by Tributing monsters from your hand and/or field whose total Levels equal 6 or more.
②: You can banish this card from your GY; Special Summon 1 non-Ritual "Archfiend" monster from your hand.

name: Maiden in Love
desc:
①: Opponent's monsters that can attack this card must attack it.
②: Cannot be destroyed by battle.
③: If this card battles an opponent's monster, at the end of the Damage Step: You can activate 1 of these effects;
● Place 1 Maiden Counter on 1 face-up monster your opponent controls.
● Take control of 1 opponent's monster with a Maiden Counter.

name: Eucalyptus Mole
desc:
You can only use the ① and ② effects of this card's name each once per turn.
①: If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower Beast monster from your Deck in face-down Defense Position, then, if this card is in Attack Position, change it to Defense Position.
②: If this card is destroyed: You can Special Summon 1 "Koala" monster or 1 "Tree Otter" from your Deck, and if you do, apply this effect until the end of the next turn.
● Non-Effect Beast monsters you control gain ATK equal to their own original DEF.

name: Illusion Gate
desc:
You can only apply the effect of this card's name once per Duel.
①: Pay half your LP; destroy as many monsters your opponent controls as possible, then you can Special Summon 1 monster from their GY to your field, ignoring its Summoning conditions.
